      "content": "wait what do you mean taper off the sertraline? i can't just stop my prescription without talking to my doctor first lol. i just meant like, can i take them at the same time? and is 900mg a lot? i thought st johns wort was pretty mild so i didn't think it would be a big deal to just add it in.",
